  <p>Hi {{username}},</p>
  <p>Great news! Someone appreciated your deal and sent you a tip:</p>
  
  <div style="border: 1px solid #eaeaea; border-radius: 8px; padding: 16px; margin: 20px 0; background-color: #f9f9f9;">
